ast.name: RPN Calculator
ast.comment: A HP-like programmable pocket calculator with a four-level stack and reverse polish notation (see http://www.hpmuseum.org/rpn.htm). Online help: Press g, ? to read the manual. This is all integrated. Web access is only needed to open the above http link directly from the help pages, not to read the manual. 2013-06-07: Fixed: Recording SF or CF not only recorded the step, but also executed it. New: RCL Î£+ recalls statistic sums into the stack registers.
